{"tid":1777031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心黑警重用］華仁附近發現炸彈後 沒引爆 反而帶回基地處理","createTime":"2019-12-10T02:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:13:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ce155c2804825a1f6130e24c05622c1e7cd4c5","tid":1777031,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9G8G2Kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9G8G2Kd.jpg&h=19f6b5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話好危險既？<br />\n<br />\n裝置可用手提電話引爆，爆炸範圍50至100米，而此類爆炸裝置，早前也曾在旺角發現過。據了解，此類釘子炸彈，若製作優良，威力十分強大，原理是將大量鐵釘混合在爆炸物中，當炸彈引爆時鐵釘會向四處射出，可以造成嚴重傷害<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20191210&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20822383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191210%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20822383&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f5687565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191210%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20822383&h=af0a09f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20191210&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20822383</a>"},{"pid":"9b892676717d894029c2423572670626cdf541b2","tid":1777031,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d6e9d7fa1bbe7d19bdb545126263f9014d49f2","tid":1777031,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日一致通過啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</sp